{"id":2,"value":"The MATE (M8) network is an AuScope-funded collection of semi-permanent telemetered broadband stations to support ongoing experiments and/or target regions of elevated research interested within Australia and its periphery. Collaborators include GSWA, GeoScience Australia, University of Tasmania, and many more to come."}
